metadata.name: HAI Energy
metadata.description:
At the heart of “HAI” is the AI Manga, that blends manga & other art styles through the use of AI. "HAI" not only reflects the Japanese word for "yes" or "I understand," but also references "AI" within the title. 'HAI Energy' explores the captivating essence of vitality that emerges during profound life transitions, encapsulating a universal deeply human experience.

Curated by DVK the artist & exhibited at Mecenate Fine Art NFT Gallery in the 'Real Thoughts' show #2 in Rome on May 24-27, 2023.
